title: RHONJ Boat Fun + RHOD + THE REAL WORLD CAST & A Jessica Detour

description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of New Jersey, which featured a boat trip and lots of tie-dye work. Then he chats Dallas, which saw the cast continue their trip. After the recaps, Danny interviews THE ENTIRE season 1 cast of THE REAL WORLD, who are reuniting on Paramount+ for a reboot. Before all of that, Danny has an important Newlyweds shawl detour.


RHONJ: 9:00ish

RHOD: 23:15ish

Real World Interview: 35:46ish
